==&amp;gt; INIT /alidata/init/fix-hosts.py
==&amp;gt; EXIT CODE: 0
==&amp;gt; INIT DEFAULT
Generating SSH1 RSA host key: [  OK  ]
Starting sshd: [  OK  ]
Starting crond: [  OK  ]
==&amp;gt; INIT DONE
==&amp;gt; RUN /home/admin/app.sh
==&amp;gt; START ...
start canal ...
start canal successful
==&amp;gt; START SUCCESSFUL ...
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
